title: Word On The Street: What is your favorite apple or pumpkin treat?
text: Word On The Street: What is your favorite apple or pumpkin treat? Comment By Compiled by Erin Dietzer Holland Sentinel By Compiled by Erin Dietzer Posted Oct. 18, 2015 at 8:00 PM By Compiled by Erin Dietzer Posted Oct. 18, 2015 at 8:00 PM Holland, Mich. "Homemade pumpkin pie and baked apples," - Marissa Ruehl, Holland. "Lemonjello's has an apple chai drink that's really good," - Sarah Harvin, Southfield. "My grandma makes a good apple crisp," - Matt Delaney, Caledonia. "I'd have to say a pumpkin spice latte," - Lindsey Carel, Holland. "Salted caramel pumpkin cheesecake bar," - Monika Dewitt Zeeland By Compiled by Erin Dietzer Holland Sentinel By Compiled by Erin Dietzer Posted Oct. 18, 2015 at 8:00 PM
